<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- فَإِنْ فَعَلَ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَجَبَ مَعَ القَضَاءِ:</span> إِطْعَامُ مِسْكِينٍ عَنْ كُلِّ يَوْمٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ مَاتَ المُفَرِّطُ وَلَوْ قَبْلَ آخَرَ:</span> أُطْعِمَ عَنْهُ كَذَلِكَ مِنْ رَأْسِ مَالِهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَلَا يُصَامُ عَنْهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> يُسَنُّ صَوْمُ التَّطَوُّعِ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> وَأَفْضَلُهُ: يَوْمٌ وَيَوْمٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَصَوْمُ ثَلَاثَةٍ مِنْ كُلِّ شَهْرٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَأَيَّامُ البِيضِ أَفْضَلُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span> ثَلَاثَ عَشْرَةَ، وَأَرْبَعَ عَشْرَةَ، وَخَمْسَ عَشْرَةَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَالخَمِيسِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَالِاثْنَيْنِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَسِتٍّ مِنْ شَوَّالٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَالأَوْلَى تَتَابُعُهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَعَقِبَ العِيدِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَصَائِمُهَا مَعَ رَمَضَانَ كَأَنَّمَا صَامَ الدَّهْرَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>